ADDITIONAL SAFETY DISCLAIMER:

This software is designed for use with lithium-ion batteries, which can be 
hazardous if mishandled. The authors and contributors of this software accept 
no responsibility for any damage, injury, or loss resulting from the use or 
misuse of this software.

Users are solely responsible for:
- Safe handling and storage of batteries
- Proper wiring and assembly of hardware
- Monitoring devices during operation
- Compliance with local safety regulations
- Proper disposal of batteries

LITHIUM BATTERIES CAN CATCH FIRE OR EXPLODE IF MISHANDLED. 
NEVER LEAVE CHARGING OR DISCHARGING BATTERIES UNATTENDED.
